Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's \cf1\b placement\cf0\b0  at 1 is the vital point.
\par
\par If Black plays at 2, White destroys the eye with 3 and after Black 4, White captures Black with 5.
\par
\par
\par }
