Dia. 02 Easy to Miss
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White can easily think that he can capture Black if he cuts at 1.
\par
\par If Black answers with 2, White plays hane at 3 and after White's placement at 5 Black can't live.
\par
\par However it is White's \cf1\b wishful thinking\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Black 2 is a wrong move. If Black plays at 5 instead of 2, Black lives.
\par }
