Dia. 03 Beginner's Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is a beginner's attack.
\par Black can live with many points at 2.
\par Up to 4, Black has a \cf1\b four space \cf0\b0 living shape.
\par
\par }
