Dia. 04 Worst Result
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \cf1\b There is death in the hane\cf0\b0 .
\par So some people might think that White 1 is the starting move.
\par However this is the \cf2\b worst result\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Black blocks with 2 and lives with many points.
\par }
